thread.title: Amanda Matler
thread.title_full: Ink Station reviewed by Amanda Matler

author: Amanda Matler
title: Amanda Matler
text: I have been using Ink Station for my ink jet cartridges for over 12 months and have always found their products to be of high quality and reasonably priced. Their service is excellent with email updates as to the status of my order. Products arrive within one to two days of ordering.
